VSivalayamNisha P. RajagopalThree CDs - Rs. 450Rajalakshmi Audio, Coimbatore, has brought out a new CD which contains a collection of songs in praise of Lord Siva in different kshetras. The selection ranges from Tirunavukkarasar's `Thevaram' to Papanasam Sivan. It also includes one each by Saint Tyagaraja and Muthuswami Dikshitar.Nisha Rajagopal brings the songs alive with all their beauty, spiritual appeal and aesthetic charm in tact.   The ragam-tanam-pallavi is a pleasant addition providing the singer an opportunity to reveal her academic strengths and Nisha has done it with a touch of class.Bottom Template Starts
